DOTFILES
========

These are my dotfiles. They configure various software that I use.

INSTALLATION
------------

    git clone https://github.com/ogllgo/dotfiles.git
    cd dotfiles
    stow [DIRECTORIES...]

where DIRECTORIES is one or more Stow packages containing the configuration
you wish to install (e.g., vim, tmux, kitty).

STRUCTURE
---------

Stow packages for configurations of software can be found within the packages/
directory. Stow is configured such that directories can be used directly as
packages; "stow vim" will manage packages/vim.

Stow should be ran from the repository's root directory.

Screenshots of the software can be found in the screenshots/ directory.

